As of the census<ref name=census2010/> of 2010, there were 165 people living in the CDP. There were 53 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] was 95.8% White, 3.0% from some other race, and 1.2% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 6.1% of the population.
